FBIS4-15119 "drsov067_g_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-067 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Some 72 Percent Said To Support Private Land Ownership Some 72 Percent Said To Support Private Land Ownership WS0704084394 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1950 GMT 7 Apr 94 WS0704084394 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Belarusian BFN [Text] According to the opinion poll conducted by the Independent Institute of Socioeconomic and Political Research, assisted by the U.S. International Center for Support of Private Entrepreneurship, 72.4 percent of those polled consider it admissble to introduce private land ownership in Belarus, while 26.6 percent oppose this. Some 20.3 percent believe that land can be owned by foreigners; 78.2 percent are opposed.
